;WITH CTE AS (
    SELECT *,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
               PARTITION BY
                    ISNULL(TemplateId,0),
                    ISNULL(GroupId,0),
                    ISNULL(Parameter1,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter2,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter3,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter4,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter5,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter6,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter7,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter8,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter9,''),
                    ISNULL(Parameter10,''),
                    ISNULL(Score,0),
                    ISNULL(CreatedBy,''),
                    ISNULL(Enabled,0),
                    ISNULL(Deleted,0),
                    ISNULL(Repeatable,0),
                    ISNULL(Category,''),
                    ISNULL(LastModifedBy,''),
                    ISNULL(qryId,0)
               ORDER BY (SELECT NULL)
           ) AS RN
    FROM HRS_QuerySyntaxes
)
SELECT COUNT(*) AS WillBeDeletedCount
FROM CTE
WHERE RN > 1;

⸻

🧠 這個數字代表什麼？

👉 「真正會被刪掉的筆數」

不是總資料量
而是：

* 每組重複資料中
* 第 2 筆開始的總和

例如：

group	總筆數	會刪
A	3	2
B	2	1
C	1	0

👉 結果 = 3

